    <p class="as-faces-note">Two of these are the cost and one is the engine. The <strong>drawdown</strong> is the fall you must be able to hold through; the real risk is selling into it. <strong>Portfolio influence</strong> is not a hazard, it is the movement that does the work, the same coin as the extra return.</p>
