        <p class="as-drift-caption as-drift-crash-caption" id="asDriftCrashCaption" hidden>A crashed path is where annual rebalancing shows its real behavior: the yearly reset buys bitcoin while it is down. Depending on the crash&rsquo;s timing and recovery, that can narrow &mdash; or reverse &mdash; the gap you saw on the smooth path. The numbers above are doing that arithmetic under your settings; neither strategy wins by default.</p>
